replies.body:
His new story is great{{sticker:sg-kiko}} 


Tries to spook the peasants by causing some errant lightning strikes only to end up having his entire grand act ignored and being accused of having caused the milk to spoil and some old cow/go lame, even as he tries to stand up for himself he gets pushed up to a wall by the superstitious farmers x)

Then he tries to spook them by telling them how he defeated some local sorcerer only for it to turn out that said sorcerer was actually terrorizing the village and the peasants realizing that decide to just let him do whatever he wants, especially defeating more local mages xD


Poor veig, he did his best to put up a magnificent scenario but everything just went wrong {{sticker:sg-miss-fortune}}
